reviewText:
Early Access Review

Good game, specially to be played with friends. Some pros and cons:

PROS:
- Good Game Mechanic;
- Fun gameplay;
- Balanced powerup gameplay;
- Workshop support (infinite levels);

CONS:
- Lobby has some issues (ranked matches with custom maps, no kick option, some game-crashing bugs)
- Custom maps easily exploitable;
- Ranking system is not the best, and not 100% balanced;
- Game is filled with bugs.

Overall, a good experience, but it might outerweight to the negative side very easily.
Since it's a UNDER DEVELOPMENT, I'll keep a watch out, and I hope they fix all the bugs and balance out the minor tweaks. Great potential, great game.

